                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190707-59-off312 t18190707-59-crimeloc314"></join>. On the 7th of June, about seven o'clock in the evening, the prisoner came to my house and wanted a lodging - he went away with a lodger of mine, returned by himself, and went up to the fire-place - he took my husband's watch off the nail, and ran away with it. I called out Stop thief! he got out of my sight, but was stopped and brought back with it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190707-59-person593">
                  THOMAS 
                  SMITH
