                     <interp inst="t18190707-59-person593" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep a coffee-shop in Liquorpond-street. I saw the prisoner running up Crown-court; he was stopped. A person said in his presence that the prisoner had run to his privy, and shut the flap down. I went to the privy, found the watch, drew it up, and gave it to Read.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 16.</p>
